Priest is willing to wait.

18
00:02:30,410 --> 00:02:31,670
If your younger sister

19
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:34,920
can wait,

20
00:02:35,610 --> 00:02:36,340
that's fine.

21
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:37,890
I don't need your reminder!

22
